{"tid":1767271,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"何文田疑發生警員開槍案 至少兩人被制服","createTime":"2019-12-03T07:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T10:07:06.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0c594f17c866d84f3b254dea04b1abd60ad14947","tid":1767271,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191203/large/1575357498_4d93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191203%2Flarge%2F1575357498_4d93.jpg&h=6a1a6399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方封鎖一段常樂街調查。梁澤岡攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191203/large/1575358628_8e69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191203%2Flarge%2F1575358628_8e69.jpg&h=a8efa43f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方曾在的士上調查。梁澤岡攝<br />\n<br />\n【15:30】消息指，警方拘捕7名疑犯<br />\n<br />\n何文田懷疑發生警員開槍事件。下午2時許，警方在何文田常樂街調查案件期間，在常樂街花園對開制服至少兩名疑犯，現場消息指警員曾經開了一槍實彈，但未有擊中人。據了解，調查案件的警員是警隊王牌之一的刑事情報科Hit Team攻擊隊員，當時正追查一宗於最近發生的金舖劫案。<br />\n<br />\n大批警員目前封鎖常樂街一段路面調，現場有客貨車及私家車的車頭均指向路邊欄杆，警員亦在一輛的士上調查，不排除曾發生追車及截車的驚險場面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191203/60337173?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191203%2F60337173%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsbvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=f30c217a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191203%2F60337173%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=40d71ea9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191203/60337173?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"8616c35c0f99549b19a8cd4d71b51cdcb8ec8b27","tid":1767271,"uid":229508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:49:56.000Z","msg":"一槍就驚？<br />\n香港啲劫匪真係冇膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe16d4c2133b37d0d6b555667702304707adf010","tid":1767271,"uid":2267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"卧底警甴去搶劫<br />\n調查科鎖定有參與遊行嘅示威者<br />\n今日突擊拉人兼且開槍殺人（可以眼界有限射咗唔知喺邊）<br />\n拉返警甴竇，卧底警甴攞啲賊贓出嚟屈 <br />\n<br />\n新聞稿：有參與遊行嘅示威者襯亂去打劫罪行，非常唔要得嘅行為，我哋要向呢班暴力同作姦犯科嘅歹徒割蓆"},{"pid":"e696d36bf1d9bf414dc2012489268bcdb4c66b2a","tid":1767271,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"黑警殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25af73b3b9367574c8c5ea3ebf25b4d27538b4a","tid":1767271,"uid":48161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T08:03:11.000Z","msg":"據了解，調查案件的警員是警隊王牌之一的刑事情報科Hit Team攻擊隊員，當時正追查一宗於最近發生的金舖劫案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/2c/T0_-1_1576764.gif/revision/latest?cb=20070417052040\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F2c%2FT0_-1_1576764.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070417052040&h=dcef4289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起徐榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3cfde0c818ff33a68cd67f31e78bdbf095d0be","tid":1767271,"uid":12265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a25af73b3b9367574c8c5ea3ebf25b4d27538b4a","tid":1767271,"uid":48161,"like":3,"dislik